<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得拦住这些石头！”罗西喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨大的石头飞快地滚向美罗城。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西用眼睛向山脚下发射激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>轰隆！地上出现了一个大坑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石头滚到了山脚，掉进坑里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了！”罗西欢呼道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那怪物去哪里了呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞过了一座山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西终于发现了巨大的脚印。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跟着脚印穿过山谷，绕过了一座高山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，罗西停住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她听到了低低的隆隆声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好像有人在打呼噜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她飞过另一座山，看到满地的野花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪物正趴在草地中央，睡在一栋大房子旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人正站在阳台上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他对着罗西眨了眨眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是火箭女孩儿吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西点点头。“你是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是纽特教授。”男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是研究爬行动物的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你为什么来这里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很疑惑。“你认识这只怪物？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它不是怪物。”纽特教授说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它是我的爬行宠物，它叫贝西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贝西？”罗西重复道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>纽特教授点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我生日的时候，朋友给了我一个神秘爬行动物的蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当这只蛋孵化以后，贝西出来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他笑了。“我没想到它会长这么大！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西皱着眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，纽特教授，贝西差点儿毁了整个美罗城！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154974</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”纽特教授说，“它一定是闻到花展的花香了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着那只巨大的爬行动物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贝西非常喜欢花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它一般只吃这儿的野花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我觉得它是想吃一些没吃过的花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它做了哪些破坏？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把贝西所做的事情告诉了纽特教授。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>教授惊呆了。“天啊！我得向布洛姆市长道歉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从现在起，我让贝西只呆在这儿的山里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝西很可爱，不过它会惹大麻烦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们还在玩儿飞盘吗？”罗西大声问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走到玛拉家的后院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到处都是水坑。玛拉和杰克全淋湿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚才有一只巨大的怪物！”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 还有，火箭女孩儿把水泼在了我们身上！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。“特勒尔不是说想去水上乐园吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔从灌木丛里跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿着用来浇花园的水管。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抓到了！”他叫道，把水浇到罗西身上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂！”罗西惊讶地叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，很快她就和朋友们一起笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这么热的天，水凉凉的感觉好极了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>